<section class="s3" id="quotes">
  <div class="s3__head">
    <h2 class="s3__heading">Practice makes progress</h2>
    <p class="s3__subhead">Testimony and outcomes</p>
  </div>

  <div class="s3__rail" id="s3Rail">

    <!-- 01 — Outcome: Maya · clay -->
    <article class="s3__card s3__card--outcome" data-surface="clay">
      <p class="s3__card-body">Negotiated IP to relaunch and funded a top 1% podcast independently, and changed her relationship with fear.</p>
      <footer class="s3__card-attribution">
        <div class="s3__card-name">Maya</div>
        <div class="s3__card-role">Journalist &amp; podcast creator</div>
      </footer>
    </article>

    <!-- 02 — Testimonial · paper -->
    <article class="s3__card s3__card--testimonial" data-surface="paper">
      <p class="s3__card-quote">I have done years of therapy and invested in personal growth. This is accelerated, transformative, and focused on my future. I have made so much progress in a year that didn't seem possible before.</p>
    </article>

    <!-- 03 — Outcome: Clara · dusk -->
    <article class="s3__card s3__card--outcome" data-surface="dusk">
      <p class="s3__card-body">Reduced social anxiety and increased energy and ease in work, resulting in a seven-figure level promotion.</p>
      <footer class="s3__card-attribution">
        <div class="s3__card-name">Clara</div>
        <div class="s3__card-role">Senior IC leader, AI / major tech</div>
      </footer>
    </article>

    <!-- 04 — Testimonial · off-a -->
    <article class="s3__card s3__card--testimonial" data-surface="off-a">
      <p class="s3__card-quote">I have discovered so much about myself, what I want, and how to work with change in a way that I now experience greater wellbeing — and also get results that change everything, in a good way.</p>
    </article>

    <!-- 05 — Outcome: Alex · moss -->
    <article class="s3__card s3__card--outcome" data-surface="moss">
      <p class="s3__card-body">Transformed consulting into a visionary leadership retreat center for climate-action decision-makers, in alignment with personal values.</p>
      <footer class="s3__card-attribution">
        <div class="s3__card-name">Alex, PhD</div>
        <div class="s3__card-role">Sustainability advisor &amp; speaker</div>
      </footer>
    </article>

    <!-- 06 — Testimonial · off-b -->
    <article class="s3__card s3__card--testimonial" data-surface="off-b">
      <p class="s3__card-quote">Working with Every Day Future feels like magic — but it's real.</p>
    </article>

    <!-- 07 — Outcome: Senior Team at YouTube · ink -->
    <article class="s3__card s3__card--outcome" data-surface="ink">
      <p class="s3__card-body">Navigated uncertainty using self-awareness through art and breathwork, and increased individual and interpersonal coherence.</p>
      <footer class="s3__card-attribution">
        <div class="s3__card-name">Senior Team</div>
        <div class="s3__card-role">at YouTube</div>
      </footer>
    </article>

    <!-- 08 — Testimonial · paper -->
    <article class="s3__card s3__card--testimonial" data-surface="paper">
      <p class="s3__card-quote">Our company and executive leadership team was struggling with significant change and we needed coaching support, fast. The techniques and results were both unexpected and exceptional.</p>
    </article>

  </div>
</section>
